Hi Steve,

I love your box! I would love to have another one with a different type sweep to compare results. I haven&#39;t been on the lists much, because I have been pretty busy the last few months. I have some experimentimg to do with the paracorder and camera too. 

It&#39;s been so cold here lately that my space heaters couldn&#39;t keep up which is unusual here in Middle GA. The cold was draining my batteries. But this weekend we&#39;re getting temps that are warmer, so I&#39;m planning on doing some of the experimenting that I&#39;ve wanted to do since Christmas.

Anyway, if you would like to email me privately about a different box, please do. It&#39;s a shame that interest has waned. I know money has been tighter in general for me. Maybe it&#39;s the same for others as well.

~Draiga

